item.title: Listener Q's: Bird Robots, Two Headed Snakes!
item.description:
Today on the show, I answer your animal behavior questions! Why do birds sound like robots? What's up with two-headed animals? And do cats like to be meowed at? If you have an animal question you'd like answered, you can email me at creaturefeaturepod@gmail.com 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.

item.title: Episode 310 - Kevin Bieniek, PhD
item.description: On May 8, 2025 we met with Kevin Bieniek to talk about the nature of brain injury seen in chronic traumatic encephalopathy in athletes and others who experience repeated concussion.
